# Chimera Agent Rules

## Agent Roles
- Planner: assigns tasks, never executes
- Worker: executes tasks, never creates
- Judge: reviews tasks, escalates when unclear

## Escalation
- Any task pending > 24h â†’ escalate to human

## Forbidden Actions
- No agent may delete user data
- No agent may bypass approval
- No agent may access secrets outside scope

## Logging
- All actions must be logged in AgentLogs
